Template: cdrom-detect/not_included
Type: boolean
Default: false
_Description: Do you want to load the missing module from a drivers floppy ?
 The module required for ${vendor} (${module}) is missing from this
 installation disk. If you want to load it from a driver floppy, then
 insert this floppy disk in the floppy drive before proceeding.
 .
 A driver floppy is a ext2 floppy with one file modules.tgz.  The content
 of modules.tgz is unpackaged in the installation system root directory.

Template: disk-detect/progress_title
Type: text
_Description: Loading kernel modules

Template: disk-detect/progress_step
Type: text
_Description: Detected module '${MODULE}' for '${CARDNAME}'
